{"tid":256970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【復牌無望？】擾攘兩年！天合化工被證監勒令停牌","createTime":"2017-05-25T01:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T01:27:53.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffddba57fa90371293d210cdb883875b326d7fa","tid":256970,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495674859_3e98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495674859_3e98.jpg&h=1bf4a66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n停牌超過兩年，兼且於今年4月份才發公告澄清沒有被勒令停牌的天合化工（1619），今早終於公布被證監會勒令停牌。<br />\n<br />\n公司於2014年上市，上市數個月就被沽空機構狙撃，其後因未能如期發布業績而於2015年3月26日停牌，中途多次就復牌進展發表公告，至上月初有消息指證監調查大摩、瑞銀及美美林協助天合化工上市事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56739261&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56739261%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170525&d=uZoqg%2FSeSQPAeDQzWqixiQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5b70c59e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56739261%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170525&h=bb51d898\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56739261&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170525</a>"}]}